Rodimus was about to push Kup out of Rockseeker&#39;s way himself when he saw him moved by a cloaked bot. He spotted the vial that was placed in that location. He waits to see the results of this action.

Kup is looking around franticly, not knowing what is going on. He doesn&#39;t even realize that a cloaked bot is with him.

Kup: What the pit just happened?!

Darkangel takes a leap at Lunekill, slashing with his swords. Lune easily knocks the swords from his hands.

Lunekill: Ok, fool, let&#39;s see what you got.

The two engage in a martial arts battle.


